which order ansible will consider cfg file
1. environment variable
2. current directory
3. home directory

default loc --  /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg

======================variables====================

string
number
boolean
list
dictionary--> {{user.name}} {{user.password}}

================variable precedance===========

group
